1.Ubuntu repositories should be updated in /etc/apt/source.list 


###### Ubuntu Main Repos
deb http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy main restricted universe multiverse 
deb-src http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy main restricted universe multiverse 

###### Ubuntu Update Repos
deb http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-security main restricted universe multiverse 
deb http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-updates main restricted universe multiverse 
deb http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-proposed main restricted universe multiverse 
deb http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-backports main restricted universe multiverse 
deb-src http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-security main restricted universe multiverse 
deb-src http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-updates main restricted universe multiverse 
deb-src http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-proposed main restricted universe multiverse 
deb-src http://in.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ saucy-backports main restricted universe multiverse 

